extendedInfo.description: Have the most complete Buenos Aires subway map and meet the most fascinating tourist attractions of this wonderful city.This application includes all the subway lines and the labels needed for better understanding of the map.Help us, be sure to rate and comment on this program.All suggestions are welcome.
